      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 73,
      "message": "This is related to a known Springboot bug that is discussed here: https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/issues/26627\n\nIt has been encountered by others when the upgraded the version of Sprintboot. I encountered it when using more recent versions of the backend image in our test deployment. The long --spring.config.location you spotted is a workaround to avoid this bug.",
